data.description: CALL LISTING AGENT DIRECT: JUSTIN OSTOW 727-667-5811.  Welcome to maintenance free living inside the beautiful guard gated paradise of Grand Hampton.  This unique garden style home has a rear entry garage and park like setting out front.  Located in the back of the community, the location provides a peaceful ambiance.  Inside features 2 story ceilings with balcony overlook, open floor plan and eat-in kitchen overlooking the family room.  The downstairs master includes a walk in closet, en-suite bathroom, dual vanities, and tiled glass shower.  Upstairs are 3 guest bedrooms and a full guest bath with tub shower combo.  Additionally there is a downstairs guest ½ bath, inside laundry room with extra storage, and upstairs bonus area/office.  Grand Hampton is a premier community with amazing clubhouse, heated pool/spa, water slide, lap pool, fitness center, playgrounds, parks, lake with dock, and basketball courts.  HOA includes full-time security, landscaping/lawn maintenance, irrigation maintenance, pest control, painting, and cable service.   All of this is located just minutes from I-75, Premium Outlet Mall, award winning dining, hospitals, and so much more.  Call for your showing today before this on is sold!  Multiple offers, highest and best due by 11:59PM on 10/15/19.
